---
title: Herby Steak Skewers with Crispy Potato Smash and Feta
description: Tender steak is best with a delicious char. We accomplish just that with these flavourful skewers. Broiling makes the process easy and makes for perfectly cooked meat and veg.  Added bonus? Adding smashed potatoes to the mix makes for golden crispy edges you'll be sure to fight over!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/brochettes-de-steak-aux-herbes-700d1527.jpg
